data.description: Gorgeous Knez Built Crestview floor plan home featuring 4 Bedrooms & 4 Bathrooms w/finished basement located in The Reserves of Willoughby. Many upgrades throughout. Beautiful landscaping & front porch greet you w/added Stone. Enter the Foyer with HDWD floors flowing into the DR that could be used as a home office space if needed. Notice the added arch details as you enter the LR accented by Stone Gas FP, 10 ft ceilings, carpet & natural light open to the Eating Area & Kitchen. Enjoy spending time in the Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Breakfast Bar, Pantry, SS Appliances, Double sink, lined w/cabinets & HDWD flooring. 1st Floor Half Bthrm w/wainscoting & HDWD floor is located off hallway heading to Attd Garage w/finished walls, opener, & drain. Admire the Wainscoting detail added to accent the stairs to the 2nd Fl w/expanded hallway leading to the conveniently placed Laundry Room w/generous storage area. Large Primary suite has multiple WI Closets, private Bthrm w/jetted tub, stall shower, double sinks & ceramic flooring. The three addt'l bedrooms have great closet spaces & Full Bthrm w/double sinks & separate area to shower so the space can be used by more than one person at a time. Oversized finished basement offers several areas to have room for a Recreation Room, play area, office, work out room or more plus a half bathroom and huge bonus areas for storage. Plenty of room out back to enjoy the large lawn area and patio. One of a kind home with upgrades & neutral decor.
